<hw>Ton</hw> <pr>(t⟦ocir⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Tone</er>.]</ety> <def>The prevailing fashion or mode; vogue;
<as>as, things of <ex>ton</ex></as>.</def> <rj><au>Byron.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
